videos.description: Jermaine Samuels says not in my house as he elevates for the massive block to deny Georgetown.
videos.headline: Jermaine Samuels swats the ball off the backboard for Villanova

videos.description: Tyler Beard pulls up and knocks down the and-1 from downtown to pull the Hoyas within five.
videos.headline: Tyler Beard drains the and-1 from beyond the arc for Georgetown

videos.description: Justin Moore muscles through his defender and knocks down the clutch and-1 to seal the victory for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Justin Moore won't be denied as he drains the and-1 for Villanova
